Extract to C:\ and Run by executing exec.bat as a admin.
The script asks for confirmation of what you would like to install and downloads the files to separate folder in "C:\Runtime_Install_Helper\" and then automatically installs the files with no user interaction and pauses after the install showing the output.
The script sets powershell script permissions to RemoteSigned and after execution returns the permissions to Resticted.

Can install directx, netfx and VC 2005 - VC 2022 + XNA 3.0 redistributable.

The space requirements are about 100MB for the downloads.
